    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128520/extras/56bac048de4aaa526dec9389c997ab57.poster.avif?t=1751031227\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128520/extras/56bac048de4aaa526dec9389c997ab57.webm?t=1751031227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128520/extras/56bac048de4aaa526dec9389c997ab57.mp4?t=1751031227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>想象一个纸箱。它的形状是否适合一到两只毛茸茸的猫咪？那五只呢？二十只呢？<br><br>Fit My Cat 为你呈现许多可爱的小猫，它们都希望坐在自己认为合适的地方。话说回来，我们的空间快用完了，我们真的在寻找一个猫咪收纳器。如果你能抽出一点时间帮忙实现这个目标，我们将不胜感激。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128520/extras/df8864019b8ac28a14369aa8efe04b81.poster.avif?t=1751031227\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128520/extras/df8864019b8ac28a14369aa8efe04b81.webm?t=1751031227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128520/extras/df8864019b8ac28a14369aa8efe04b81.mp4?t=1751031227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>每一只猫都经过训练并且善于空间管理——你可以随意拿起它们并旋转它们。<br><br>请注意，一些纸箱可能会附带毛线球或整个猫屋，但这并不会阻止这些精力充沛的小猫们试图钻进去。<br><br>测试你的技能，向世界展示赶猫入箱的乐趣从这里开始！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128520/extras/00604ac1f1757bac32bbc5a14c5cfd6e.poster.avif?t=1751031227\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128520/extras/00604ac1f1757bac32bbc5a14c5cfd6e.webm?t=1751031227\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3128520/extras/00604ac1f1757bac32bbc5a14c5cfd6e.mp4?t=1751031227\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>主要特色：<br><br>超过90个精彩的关卡，等着被毛茸茸填满的纸箱<br>许多形状、颜色和大小各异的完美猫咪<br>喵嗷般美妙的音乐配乐",
